snippet.title: UNLOVED Clinic Upgrade Official Trailer
snippet.description:
New Trailer for the upcoming content upgrade in October: The Clinic!

The new content features a new weapon - the Silenced Machine Pistol, two new enemy types - the Demon Nurse and the Lobotomized Doctor, new Music by James Dean and of course the new location itself - the Clinic.

This new upgrade will be available in October 2015!

If you like this video, please click the like button and share it with your friends, so the UNLOVED community can grow. Thank you very much!

UNLOVED on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/321270
My website: http://www.paulinthenet.de
